                <h2>Privacy</h2>
                <div class="alert alert-info">
                    This service uses calls to the YouTube Data API.
                </div>
                <p>This service does not share any personal data with third parties.</p>
                <p>
                    Any personal data transferred to the service may temporarily be limited and available in memory as access logs,
