                </p>
                <p>
                    Instances of data, personal or otherwise, logged temporarily by this service are:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Accessed server URI (e.g., <code>/api/list</code>) even for missing (404) pages</li>
                    <li>Playlist ID</li>
                    <li>User agent</li>
                </ul>
                <p>
                    <strong>None of this data is shared with third party</strong> except "<strong>Playlist ID</strong>", which is
