                    No Google log-in is required or optional for the usage of this tool.
                    No Google account information will or can be obtained or used by this tool.
                </p>
                <p>
                    This service does not place any data on your device besides the PHP session cookie, which is
                    necessary. No first or third party <b>tracking</b> cookies or local storage are used or abused when accessing information
                    with or on this website. By using or viewing this website, you agree to this usage.
                </p>
